title.value: Изготовление вакцины живой против реовирусного теносиновита птиц с использованием СПФ-эмбрионов кур  и ее иммунологические свойства
Preparation of live vaccine against avian reovirus tenosynovitis with the use of SPF-embryos of chicken and its immunological properties

journal.title: Epizootiology, Immunobiology, Pharmacology, Sanitary Science : international scientific and practical journal

person.name: Radyush, I.S., National Academy of Sciences. Scientific and Practical Center of Animal Breding (Belarus). The S.N. Vyshelesskij Inst. of Experimental Veterinary Medicine

abstract.value: In the conditions of the Republic of Belarus there was presented results of development of a vaccine against avian reovirus tenosynovitis using SPF-chicken embryos. This article deals with the way of avian reovirus tenosynovitis life vaccine production with help of SPF-chicken embryos. The results prove that chickens being vaccinated with the experimental series of the above mentioned vaccine in the age of 7 and 35 days. On the 21st day after the first vaccination have antibodies in titer 1728,6+/-141, on the 7th, 14th, 21st and 30th day after the second vaccination antibodies titer in blооd definitely increases relative to antibodies titer on the 21st day after the first vaccination and gets to 2433+/-239, 2095,6+/-253,7, 2587+/-293,9 and 2574,8+/-263,0 accordingly. This fact proves of high-level immunity maturation and high immunogenic vaccine activity. The obtained data proved the formation of expressed immunity and high immunogenic activity of the strain of avian reovirus tenosynovitis 'S1133'.
